node.text: I’ve always been so in awe of these 3 guys for everything they stand for. They’re literally hero’s for everyone on our roster! It was an honor to sit and talk with them. Catch my episode of #newdaypod on @applepodcasts @spotifypodcasts now!

node.text: We love you Daff. Thank you for opening your arms/doors to me and SO many others during our time of need. I can’t begin to explain the impact you’ve had on us. I’m going to miss you ❤️ And I want to say to anyone reading this if you or someone you know ever feel alone, lost or have thoughts of suicide, please know there is help. #screamqueen

node.text:
Happy Birthday Flexy 😭😍🥰
No words or pictures will ever do justice for how much I love this 8 year old puppy soul boy! Big boy! Flex has traveled all over the country with us and changed my life forever. America’s dog! Flex, if you’re reading this from your iBone since apparently all dogs have an IG, I love you more than you’ll ever know!! Stay kyoot ❤️✌🏼
